Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了小夏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.12,0:06:21.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么突然吐槽了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:23.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要画设计图呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.93,0:06:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才我们在设计什么东西呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.25,0:06:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来只要拼起来就可以了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.29,0:06:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们打钉子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:32.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边这么顺利呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:36.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 这种时候不冷静的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就想不到好主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主意 主意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.89,0:06:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲酱家里 厕所门上不是有个把手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.28,0:06:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个怎么看都像只鸭子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:07:00.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢 小夏想到什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:01.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.41,0:07:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.45,0:07:06.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越用力想 越是什么都想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.70,0:07:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么新奇的主意…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.69,0:07:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非小夏 真的觉得我什么都没想到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.79,0:07:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才我一直在装没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.21,0:07:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是开个玩笑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.69,0:07:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜欢思考这种尖端科技了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.26,0:07:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲酱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事情就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.10,0:07:31.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是折刀的刀柄部分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.06,0:07:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 自信爆表啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.13,0:07:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者 如果你叫我『会走路的活字典』我会很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:40.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活字典本来就会走路的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.51,0:07:43.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先我来划线做标记
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.66,0:07:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏用锯子沿线锯木板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.54,0:07:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锯完之后要做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.85,0:07:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按我说的顺序钉上钉子固定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.25,0:07:57.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先用那块板作为底座
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:08:00.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那块大板立起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.28,0:08:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中间一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.18,0:08:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右边一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 这是莲酱想出来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.48,0:08:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连我都觉得做得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.45,0:08:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲酱 这是用来干什么的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.70,0:08:23.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我现在就用一下看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要睡觉啊 还管不管！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 最后做成这样了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.35,0:09:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 书架
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.76,0:09:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这气味…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.48,0:09:14.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是咖喱呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:15.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我要开始上菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.21,0:09:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学校的咖喱和莲华…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个组合…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过莲华应该不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.63,0:09:28.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做梦也想不到本校会发生那种大悲剧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.52,0:09:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.77,0:09:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那次呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:39.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下课啦 下课啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.96,0:09:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去玩积木
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:44.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小吉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能把娃娃带到学校呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.51,0:09:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小吉先生没问题呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.56,0:09:54.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上课的时候是收起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.73,0:09:57.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被老师看到的话要没收的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.84,0:10:01.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师说过上课的时候不要玩就没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.40,0:10:05.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 今天日影休息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.19,0:10:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是感冒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明昨天还是活蹦乱跳的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.94,0:10:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 今天的午饭是咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.97,0:10:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日影那份也可以吃掉了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 好歹稍微关心下日影呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那木实就只有一份咖喱了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.80,0:10:27.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不行 我也很想多吃咖喱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.53,0:10:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.22,0:10:32.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曹操到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.97,0:10:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来得好晚呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.63,0:10:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了点麻烦事所以迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.05,0:10:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影姐 迟到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.81,0:10:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又没什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:47.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不~行呀 不~行呀 我~要告诉老~师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.01,0:10:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是小孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.76,0:10:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小孩子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影姐背着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.23,0:11:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日影 学校不准带那种东西的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.82,0:11:03.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被老师看到的话要没收的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦 在动呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.27,0:11:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们把我家妹妹当成什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.32,0:11:10.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父母发烧去医院了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我在学校照顾她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.60,0:11:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才迟到了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.46,0:11:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话请假不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.22,0:11:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的午餐是咖喱 所以不能请假
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.62,0:11:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切 竟然记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.03,0:11:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么卖零食的 给
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.27,0:11:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师说了 年纪最大的卖零食的要负责照顾莲华
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.20,0:11:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.06,0:11:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么呀 这种事情木实更适合做呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.95,0:11:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你这么说 决定好的事情也不会改了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.47,0:11:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了哦大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.10,0:11:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂木实
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来来 小夏和小鞠一起来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.48,0:11:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛君也过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 不要逃呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.18,0:11:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 抱抱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我抱也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.05,0:11:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会哄小孩子 真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.23,0:12:01.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.43,0:12:10.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咬我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.32,0:12:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲华见到有兴趣的东西就会咬哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是很好吗 她很喜欢你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.72,0:12:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湿嗒嗒的 我要去洗一下校服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:21.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:24.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲华的奶嘴掉地上了 我也要去洗一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:25.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.66,0:12:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.49,0:12:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我要创造积木高度的新纪录
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.54,0:12:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏加油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.60,0:12:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 那两个人把小孩丢下跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.59,0:12:54.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 这孩子已经会走路了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.78,0:12:55.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.63,0:12:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.43,0:13:02.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的过来了呀 好可爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.06,0:13:04.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏海的最高纪…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的最高纪录…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.74,0:13:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的最高纪录…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.43,0:13:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只剩下一块了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.16,0:13:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏海 一点小事哭什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:32.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家之后我把零食分你一半吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.05,0:13:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害呢 小鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.03,0:13:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经三年级了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.14,0:13:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点小事当然…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.13,0:13:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小吉先生小吉先生 小吉先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.24,0:13:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小吉先生湿嗒嗒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:00.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鞠冷静点…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.51,0:14:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了怎么了 发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:06.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了很多事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.79,0:14:08.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲华她… 咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.06,0:14:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明刚才还在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.96,0:14:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.65,0:14:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非去走廊了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走廊里没看见呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.32,0:14:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.18,0:14:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进配膳室了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.10,0:14:22.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是叫人操心…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在干什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.11,0:14:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是主菜桶 你准备对咖喱做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.13,0:14:32.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲华把咖喱当成人质… 咖喱质了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.07,0:14:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲华 Stop Stop
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖喱…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.59,0:15:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家好期待的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.19,0:15:06.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖喱…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.82,0:15:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖喱咖喱咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.32,0:15:12.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待很久的咖喱…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:20.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖喱咖喱咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.53,0:15:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样 莲酱第一次上学就把学校镇压下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.22,0:15:32.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法忘记那个瞬间呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.12,0:15:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.68,0:15:47.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲戚送的梨子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.77,0:15:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.62,0:15:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞌睡防止装置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.41,0:15:56.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是莲华做的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.79,0:15:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个要怎么用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.84,0:15:59.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.88,0:16:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扫卫生差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.55,0:16:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,书得放好才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.01,0:16:27.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛 踩到什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.36,0:16:32.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 那是什么呀 弹力球吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.19,0:16:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是弹力球吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.81,0:16:36.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.79,0:16:45.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小吉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像比以前更破了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.03,0:16:51.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破成这样不能要了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.67,0:16:53.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.71,0:16:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能帮忙找下我的弹力球吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.07,0:16:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,踩到的话会很痛 所以要小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.30,0:17:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.13,0:17:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那表情怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和体检完之后的表情一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.23,0:17:07.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我踩到你的弹力球了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.82,0:17:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要随便跑进我的房间玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来在那里呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.44,0:17:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我给我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.39,0:17:14.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.07,0:17:18.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是宝物的话为什么会丢在我的房间呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是丢在这
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.31,0:17:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是刚好找到以前喜欢的弹力球 丢着玩而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不还是在丢么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.24,0:17:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.53,0:17:31.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我出去玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.79,0:17:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.13,0:17:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 接下来要做什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.10,0:17:38.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 要把书收拾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.16,0:17:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相册？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么时候的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很老的照片了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.12,0:17:54.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过为什么我脸上有伤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.77,0:18:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.16,0:18:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得是小吉先生掉到门外 去捡的时候摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.78,0:18:50.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.87,0:18:53.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.98,0:18:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 没预先联系就过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:18:57.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在方便吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:19:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 外面很热呢 进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.60,0:19:03.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.67,0:19:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.80,0:19:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.43,0:19:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤好像做了不少我的布娃娃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.35,0:19:13.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地上什么都没有却摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.58,0:19:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对对… 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:20.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擅自做的那些布娃娃果然还是很糟糕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不糟糕呀 做得很好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.29,0:19:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:29.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小时候喜欢的娃娃变成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:32.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想让你教我怎么样把它补好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:35.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裁 裁缝工具在我的房间…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.14,0:19:38.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可以进萤的房间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.00,0:19:41.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也带了裁缝工具过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.11,0:19:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 我的房间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.64,0:19:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那个 前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.38,0:19:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做了这么多呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.63,0:19:59.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤真的很喜欢娃娃呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.57,0:20:01.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这方面很像个小学生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.71,0:20:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.29,0:20:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过呀 也不要只做我的娃娃 做点其他人的娃娃怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:11.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都做一样的很无聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.08,0:20:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 不会无聊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.32,0:20:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我会的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.11,0:20:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么这个娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.95,0:20:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样才能补好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.59,0:20:22.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:24.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经破得很厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.65,0:20:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是觉得用新布重新做一个可能会更好…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.57,0:20:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话就会变成另一个娃娃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.83,0:20:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就要打补丁了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.18,0:20:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后该怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.19,0:20:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 那里应该…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.49,0:20:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 感觉不错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.01,0:20:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤做得好快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.72,0:20:55.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.02,0:20:56.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈 没事吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.45,0:21:04.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先走了 萤下次来我家玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.68,0:21:07.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 一路小心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.36,0:21:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 吃晚饭了 来拿餐具吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.88,0:21:41.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.96,0:21:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 那个弹力球怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.85,0:21:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放回壁橱的玩具箱里面了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.81,0:21:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心不要再丢掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.65,0:21:54.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然后悔也没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.06,0:21:55.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.28,0:21:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么突然学起大人说话来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.73,0:21:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是大人了呀
Comment: 0,0:23:38.50,0:23:40.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,(ED)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.50,0:23:43.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧急呼救吗 这是紧急呼救吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.29,0:23:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.34,0:23:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏 Stop
